1) Install Windows 7 64bit.

2) Install MSYS2 from https://msys2.github.io/.

3) Start "MSYS2 Shell".

4) Run as follows.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
$ update-core
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

5) Restart "MSYS2 Shell".

6) Run as follows.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
$ pacman -Su
$ pacman -S VCS base-devel mingw-w64-x86_64-toolchain mingw-w64-x86_64-clutter-gst mingw-w64-x86_64-gst-libav mingw-w64-x86_64-gst-plugins-bad mingw-w64-x86_64-gst-plugins-good mingw-w64-x86_64-gst-plugins-ugly
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

7) Start "MinGW-w64 Win64 Shell".

8) Run as follows.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
$ git clone https://bitbucket.org/ohhara/ohmultivideoplayer.git
$ cd ohmultivideoplayer
$ ./configure
$ make
$ ./omvp
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
